{"tid":815862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾百河北江西老兵　徒步闖向天安門","createTime":"2018-09-12T10:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T06:40:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ee6fa1ead01e67e48525b07921cbb9dbc6890b57","tid":815862,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180912/20497485\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180912%2F20497485&d=eglcHZo5bQlIHxwLRU4D2jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=6db57249\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180912%2F20497485&h=21a68087\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180912/20497485</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月12日 <br />\n<br />\n逾百河北江西老兵　徒步闖向天安門<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180912/large/12ch104p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180912%2Flarge%2F12ch104p.jpg&h=1a8d4a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前日逾千老兵到四川省政府上訪示威，一度與警察衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地退役老兵維權事件此起彼落。繼前日逾千老兵在成都通宵包圍四川省政府請願，昨日又有消息指，逾百位河北和江西的老兵，擺脫當局控制後，昨日徒步向天安門行進；但結果如何不詳。傳北京多個國家機關都有老兵聚集請願示威，儼成浪潮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成都老兵昨晨解散<br />\n<br />\n網上消息指，逾千老兵9月10日成都維權包圍省政府，行動震撼全城，但匆匆收場，無果而終。經老兵代表與副省長王一宏會談後，昨日凌晨兩點左右老兵全部解散，各自回家。王承諾本月24日前給予老兵們答覆。<br />\n<br />\n昨日上午有網民在社交網推特貼出一段視頻，指100多名來自河北和江西老兵，擺脫久敬莊（北京收留上訪人士的集中營）控制後，正徒步向天安門行進。但至昨晚再無有關他們的消息。另有一段視頻是一名男子昨上午在天安門附近直播，自稱叫李澤（音），「我在尋找來自全國各地的戰友」。 <br />\n<br />\n網傳視頻還顯示，數十名河北籍老兵在北京中南海圍牆外舉行靜坐，警方到場維穩。有消息說今年3月新成立的退役軍人事務部外面和中央軍委周邊，也有大批老兵聚集上訪。這些消息均未得到官方證實。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter/美國之音  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n傳報道踩中共紅線　網易財經遭整改"},{"pid":"32725a7bb2f0c24379081123c8842f9f8a5ed189","tid":815862,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T11:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea16d02b700f9491baa7a740793c9c3e4ccb021c","tid":815862,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T12:10:03.000Z","msg":"昨日兇手, 今日「老兵」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sohcradio.com/Media/2015/03/24/20150324_0933_1501301607592436--ss2_61445-sm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohcradio.com%2FMedia%2F2015%2F03%2F24%2F20150324_0933_1501301607592436--ss2_61445-sm.jpg&h=12fb1866&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3f460ad8c60df09d325dc94e8b1e9514e724092","tid":815862,"uid":53705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ea16d02b700f9491baa7a740793c9c3e4ccb021c","tid":815862,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T12:10:03.000Z","msg":"昨日兇手, 今日「老兵」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sohcradio.com/Media/2015/03/24/20150324_0933_1501301607592436--ss2_61445-sm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohcradio.com%2FMedia%2F2015%2F03%2F24%2F20150324_0933_1501301607592436--ss2_61445-sm.jpg&h=12fb1866&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"呢班老兵可以再一次參與 屠殺<br />\n<br />\n不過角色調轉左<br />\n以前佢地係屠殺一方<br />\n<br />\n今日是 被屠殺一方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf646ca83f1e1cc4c54711032119c7e89a7dd8c5","tid":815862,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:08:48.000Z","msg":"人必自侮而人侮之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49689084486a0413f9d46e22182336200d5f823c","tid":815862,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:09:33.000Z","msg":"用完即棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138a3ebf468d1f532d4